            <scopecontent id="aspace_3c1ad5dfafef16078ffbc10db1a2a8ad">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>This series includes personal correspondence between Maxine and Victor Kumin and Susannah Colt as well as black and white photographs of Maxine Kumin.</p>
               <p>Materials also include correspondence from Victor Kumin reflecting on the 50-year anniversary of the dropping of the atom bomb, as well as photographs from when Victor Kumin was stationed in Los Alamos as an army scientist on the Manhattan Project.</p>
            </scopecontent>
